wide across eyes and 
<quantity id="5B719B781360541AFCF3FD5575CBE394" box="[855,941,727,751]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" unit="mm" value="1.7">1.7 mm</quantity>
wide across hind margins of pronotum.
</paragraph>
